<refsect1 id="VS-U-4a">
<title>Preliminaries</title>
<itemizedlist mark="bullet">
    <listitem>The Digest HTTP authentication can have the attributes kept between sessions.</listitem>
    <listitem>If the target browser supports the Digest authentication, the opaque attribute can be used for the session id.</listitem>
    <listitem>The Virtuoso server has a predefined authentication hook for digest authentication.</listitem>
    <listitem>Digest authentication is held in WS.WS.DIGEST_AUTH.</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</refsect1>
</refentry>
